        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          10. What levels of protective marking are likely to apply to the service?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          This is to be confirmed through the project though is likely to be Official. There may be a requirement for higher classification which would be scoped as part of the discovery.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          11. Is it possible for the Authority to share more information about the senior business user for the Disinformation Data Platform and their objectives for the assignment?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          The objective for the project is to provide a shared view of the disinformation threats across departments to inform better responses to the threat. The primary objectives of the project are to:<br>Improve HMG’s understanding of the threat of disinformation and therefore its ability to respond effectively;<br>Improve counter-disinformation data sharing across relevant government stakeholders;<br>Improve consistency and effectiveness of government analysis of counter-disinformation data; and<br>Improve counter-disinformation threat information sharing with wider Government Departments.
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          12. What delivery approaches, i.e. Lean-Agile, SAFe, etc is the Authority using that are likely to apply to this assignment?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
          This is a new requirement with no pre existing delivery approaches.  It would be for the delivery partner to propose their approach. We expect suppliers to align to practices and principles that enable continuous, user-centred product delivery in a complex environment. As such, your proposed delivery approach must cope well with ambiguity and be highly responsive and change-tolerant
        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          13. Can the Authority confirm any interfaces that the Disinformation Data Platform is likely to have – notwithstanding the fact that discovery has yet to take place?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
