        </dd>
        
      </div>
    
  
    
      <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
        <dt class="govuk-summary-list__key">
          18. We hold Cyber Essentials Plus accreditation but we are not ISO27001 certified, is that a PASS or FAIL against the proposal criteria?
        </dt>
        <dd class="govuk-summary-list__value">
